'''Christian Alzmann''' is a senior art director at [[Industrial Light & Magic]]. He drew the [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]] and [[Darth Maul/Legends|Darth Maul]] cover art for [[Star Wars Insider 88|''Star Wars Insider'' 88]], and was a concept artist on ''[[Rogue One: A Star Wars Story]]'' as well as ''[[Star Wars: The Mandalorian]]'', where he was responsible for designing [[Din Grogu|Grogu]].

